                            <comment id="15894493" author="till.rohrmann" created="Fri, 3 Mar 2017 14:49:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This should also be relevant for &lt;tt&gt;1.3.0&lt;/tt&gt;, right?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
